    🐛 fix IDOR: filter GetNotificationsSince by userID in pushCatchUpSummary (#14373)
    
    pushCatchUpSummary streamed all users'notifications to the SSE-connected
    user. Add GetUserNotificationsSince that filters by user_id and use it in
    the catch-up handler. Internal batch callers (observer, scheduler) keep
    using the unfiltered variant since they process all users in batch jobs.
    
